'''Hurom''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Thule/Legends|Thule]]. Located in the center of the city was an ancient [[Sith temple (Hurom)|Sith Temple]] which continued to attract devotees for thousands of [[Standard year/Legends|years]] following the [[Great Sith War/Legends|Great Sith War]]. Much of the population spoke some dialect of the ancient [[Sith (language)|Sith]]. It was believed that many of the buildings in Hurom were older than some other civilizations, having been built to military standards.

